类 IntStream

    IntBernoulli, IntConst, IntDiscretized, IntDistribution, IntEmpirical, IntUniformAllInts, IntUniformRange

    public abstract class IntStream
extends DblStream
    A stream of integer numbers, usually the sequence is produced by a pseudo random number generator. This classes' nextInt()-method returns an int-value in the interval [min(),max()], i.e. including both min() and max(). This is an abstract base class.
    作者:
    Torsten Hildebrandt
